Recorded in Public Records 7/12/2021 8:27 AM OR Book 8571 Page 1716,
Instrument #2021076035, Pam Childers Clerk of the Circuit Court Escambia
County, FL Recording $10.00
PREPARED BY: Brad Calhoun
5756 Orange St
Milton, FL 32570
WARNING!
THIS LEGAL DOCUMENT REFLECTS THAT A CONSTRUCTION LIEN
HAS BEEN PLACED ON THE REAL PROPERTY LISTED HEREIN. UNLESS
THE OWNER OF SUCH PROPERTY TAKES ACTION TO SHORTEN THE
TIME PERIOD, THIS LIEN MAY REMAIN VALID FOR ONE YEAR FROM
THE DATE OF RECORDING, AND SHALL EXPIRE AND BECOME NULL
AND VOID THEREAFTER UNLESS LEGAL PROCEEDINGS HAVE BEEN
COMMENCED TO FORECLOSE OR TO DISCHARGE THIS LIEN.
State of Florida
County of Escambia
CLAIM OF LIEN
Before me, the undersigned notary public, personally appeared Stephen B. Calhoun,
Manager of Bradley Homes, LLC, a Florida limited liability company, who was duly sworn
and says that he is the lienor herein, whose address is 5756 Orange Street, Milton, Florida 32570,
and that in accordance with a contract with 5740 TURKEY RD TRUST 11/01/2020, lienor
furnished labor, services, materials, and specially painting, drywall, flooring, air conditioning
system, roofing, decks, landscaping, electrical and plumbing fixtures on the real property located
at 5740 Turkey Rd, Pensacola, FL 32526, in Escambia County, Florida, more particularly
described as:
BEG AT THE NE COR OF SEC 36 N 72 DEG 25 MIN 52 SEC W ALG N LI OF SEC 2678 23/100 FT TO PT OF
INTER WITH NLY PROJECTION OF ELY R/W OF TURKEY ST S 18 DEG 19 MIN 53 SEC W ALG ELY R/W
LI OF TURKEY ST 921 82/100 FT FOR POB S 71 DEG 43 MIN 36 SEC E 273 47/100 FT S 18 DEG 39 MIN 18
SEC W 83 73/100 FT N 71 DEG 55 MIN 50 SEC W 273 FT TO E R/W LI TURKEY ST N 18 DEG 19 MIN 53
SEC E ALG SD R/W 84 70/100 FT TO POB OR 7439 P 851
for a total value of $39.831.42, of which there remains unpaid $20,693.30. The first of the items
was delivered on the 6th day of February, 2021, and the last of the items was delivered to the
above-described property on the 16th day of April, 2021.
Stephen B. Calhoun, manager
Bradley Homes, LLC
SWORN TO AND SUBSCRIBED before me this the | 2"" day of July, 2021, by
Stephen B. Calhoun as manager of Bradley Homes, LLC, who appeared before me by means
of physical presence
and
who

personally

to

FL DL
as identification.
Ashley Danner
Notary Public
Comm.#HH075772
Expires: Dec. 29, 2024
Bonded Thru Aaron Notary
